~~~ 
<h3 id="1">1: Add comment in Project.toml</h3>
tags: <i>test, julia</i> <br/>
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='name = ":[name]"' 

rewrite='''
# A new comment.
name = ":[name]"'''
</code></pre>
~~~

~~~ 
<h3 id="2">2: Replace var === nothing</h3>
tags: <i>julia</i> <br/>
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='if :[var] === nothing' 

rewrite='if isnothing(:[var])'
</code></pre>
~~~

